article.description: Juvaris Hayes registered 14 points, eight assists and six rebounds as Merrimack topped Army 69-60 on Wednesday night.
article.headline: Hayes carries Merrimack over Army 69-60
article.story: NORTH ANDOVER, Mass. -- Juvaris Hayes registered 14 points, eight assists and six rebounds as Merrimack topped Army 69-60 on Wednesday night. Mikey Watkins had 17 points for Merrimack (6-5). Devin Jensen added 14 points. Jaleel Lord had eight rebounds for the hosts. Tommy Funk had 18 points for the Black Knights (4-5). Matt Wilson added 18 points and 11 rebounds. Lonnie Grayson had seven assists. Merrimack plays UC Santa Barbara on the road next Sunday. Army matches up against Buffalo on the road on Saturday. --- For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP-Top25 --- This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
